OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,FA man who died at a summer solstice
OL,7,Fevent at a Bronze Age stone circle in
OL,8,Fthe Peak District has been named as
OL,9,FIsaac Clare-Watts from Nottingham.
OL,11,FDerbyshire Police officer were called
OL,12,Fto reports of a man's body being found
OL,13,Fat Nine Ladies Stone Circle in Stanton
OL,14,FLees at 1.38pm on Monday 22 June.
OL,16,FThe 26-year-old was pronounced dead at
OL,17,Fthe scene. Police say their thoughts
OL,18,Fremain with Isaac's family.
OL,20,FA 41-year-old man arrested on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of murder remains in custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
