OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,FIn a previous statement, the Peak
OL,7,FDistrict National Park Authority said:
OL,8,F"We have been made aware of the tragic
OL,9,Fnews and the investigation is being
OL,10,Fhandled by our colleagues at the East
OL,11,FMidlands Special Operations Unit.
OL,13,F"Our condolences are with the young
OL,14,Fman's family during this difficult
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
