CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782478095
OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,FOfficers have said a number of people
OL,7,Fwere in the area over the weekend for
OL,8,Fthe summer solstice and are urging
OL,9,Fanyone who was there between June 19
OL,10,Fand 23, and anyone who has any video
OL,11,Ffootage from the event during the same
OL,12,Ftime period, to come forward.
OL,14,FThe force is also asking anyone with
OL,15,Fdashcam footage of vehicles arriving
OL,16,Fand leaving over the weekend to
OL,17,Fcontact officers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
