PN,34404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782478095
OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Tony Owen, from
OL,7,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,8,FUnit (EMSOU), who is leading the
OL,9,Finvestigation, said previously: "I am
OL,10,Furgently appealing for anyone who
OL,11,Fattended the summer solstice event
OL,12,Fover the weekend to please speak to
OL,13,Fofficers as soon as they can.
OL,15,F"A young man's life has been taken in
OL,16,Fthe most brutal way so it is vital
OL,17,Fthat myself and the team build up a
OL,18,Fclear picture of the exact
OL,19,Fcircumstances surrounding his death.
OL,26,@qD@aOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782478095
OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,F"This is why we urgently need to speak
OL,7,Fto everyone who was at the scene over
OL,8,Fthe weekend.
OL,10,F"You may have only been there briefly
OL,11,Fand think you can't help, but you
OL,12,Fcould hold the key piece of
OL,13,Finformation we need to understand what
OL,14,Fhas happened and help us to get
OL,15,Fjustice for this young man's family.
OL,17,F"So I would ask, please, that if you
OL,18,Fattended the event, you contact us
OL,19,Furgently so we can build up a picture
OL,20,Fof the event itself and what has led
OL,21,Fto this man's death.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782478095
OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,F"I also really urge anyone who
OL,7,Fcaptured video footage from the event
OL,8,Fover the weekend to please come
OL,9,Fforward.
OL,11,F"You could play a key role in helping
OL,12,Fus with this murder investigation."
OL,14,FDerby Mountain Rescue Team, which was
OL,15,Fcalled out to assist East Midlands
OL,16,FAmbulance Service at the scene, said
OL,17,Fin a statement on Facebook: "Our
OL,18,Fthoughts are with the man's friends
OL,19,Fand family at this difficult time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@cO]yD@]OU{D@cO]
