OL,3,CMan who died at stone circle summer
OL,4,Csolstice event named
OL,6,FAccording to English Heritage, Nine
OL,7,FLadies Stone Circle is a small early
OL,8,FBronze Age stone circle "traditionally
OL,9,Fbelieved to depict nine ladies turned
OL,10,Fto stone as a penalty for dancing on
OL,11,FSunday".
OL,13,FA woman who visited the historic site
OL,14,Ffor the solstice said the news was
OL,15,F"very sad and upsetting", adding she
OL,16,Fbelieves there should be more of a
OL,17,Fpresence of medical organisations for
OL,18,Fsuch events, such as the St John
OL,19,FAmbulance first aid charity.
OL,26,@pD@YOUsD@GO]wD@AOUwD@XO]
